{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:0","text":"这个 command line tool 由 engine 使用，用于自动启动和停止后端 PostgreSQL relational database server。Site admins 也可以使用它执行各种 database maintenance tasks。"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:1","text":"Usage: tractor-dbctl [options]（用法）"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:2","text":"Options（选项）："}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:3","text":"Option（选项）"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:4","text":"Description（说明字段内容）"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:5","text":"--start-for-engine"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:6","text":"启动 postgresql server，并按 db.config 中的配置自动 build/upgrade schema（engine 使用）"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:7","text":"--stop-for-engine"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:8","text":"按 db.config 中的配置停止 postgresql server（engine 使用）"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:9","text":"--start"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:10","text":"启动 postgresql 数据库 server"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:11","text":"--stop"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:12","text":"停止 postgresql server；如果 engine 无法自动完成停止，或 postgresql server 是手动启动的，可以用它关闭 postgresql；engine 正在运行时不要执行此命令。"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:13","text":"--status"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:14","text":"检查 postgresql server 的状态"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:15","text":"--init"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:16","text":"初始化 postgresql data directory；server 必须未运行"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:17","text":"--build"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:18","text":"构建 tractor database；server 必须正在运行"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:19","text":"--destroy"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:20","text":"移除 postgres database directory；server 必须未运行；这会移除"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:21","text":"所有"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:22","text":"当前和历史 job 与 blade information。"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:23","text":"--upgrade"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:24","text":"更新 database schema 数据库结构"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:25","text":"--check-upgrade"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:26","text":"检查是否需要 upgrades"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:27","text":"--no-auto-upgrade"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:28","text":"阻止 database schema 数据库结构自动 upgrade 升级"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:29","text":"--purge-jobs"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:30","text":"移除所有 jobs"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:31","text":"--vacuum"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:32","text":"重建未删除 jobs 的 tables 以节省空间"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:33","text":"--reset-job-counter"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:34","text":"重置 job id counter，使 job ids（jids）从 1 开始；只能与 --purge-jobs 一起使用"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:35","text":"--show-params"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:36","text":"显示存储在 database 中的 configuration parameters"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:37","text":"--update-params"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:38","text":"将 config files 中定义的某些 configuration parameters 推送到 database"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:39","text":"--logs-usage"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:40","text":"报告 postgresql log files 使用的 disk space"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:41","text":"--purge-logs"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:42","text":"移除 postgresql 日志 log files 文件"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:43","text":"--backup=filename"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:44","text":"将 backup 写入指定 file；server 必须未运行。"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:45","text":"--restore=filename"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:46","text":"从指定 backup file 恢复 database；server 必须未运行"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:47","text":"--config-dir=path"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:48","text":"tractor config directory 的配置 path 路径"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:49","text":"--quiet,"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:50","text":"--q"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:51","text":"除 errors 外，抑制所有 output"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:52","text":"--verbose,"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:53","text":"-v"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:54","text":"调整 verbosity 详细程度级别"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:55","text":"--debug,"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:56","text":"-d"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:57","text":"打印 debug messages 调试消息"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:58","text":"--help,"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:59","text":"-h"}
{"item_id":"4184a1c17c:60","text":"显示此 message"}
